race.description: Lees Orchard Tassie Gold Apple Ht1 Standing Pace
race.comment: STAR MAJOR (9) won at this track two runs ago before finishing third at his latest appearance over 1609m at Hobart, beaten 5 metres. Stepping up a level this time but on his best form he is capable of taking this out. GLENLEDI ELVIS NZ (8) was once again right in the mix last start when runner-up over 2090m at Hobart, beaten 10 metres. Finds a tougher race but a win is not out of the question. DE GOEY (7) finished second at this track last time. Consistent performer whose best form stacks up favourably so he must be included. KEAYANG FITZY (10) has been about the mark of late and must be respected, the latest offering a sound second at Hobart over 1609m.
